Class MapMenuWidgetFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.tak.platform.widgets.factory.MapMenuWidgetFactory
  • public class MapMenuWidgetFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Factory for creating IMapMenuWidgets. The MenuLayoutWidget will use this factory for MapLayoutWidget.openMenuOnItem.
